1049
01:07:29,200 --> 01:07:30,080
Hey, kid!

1050
01:07:32,480 --> 01:07:35,120
Strike three! What the hey?

1051
01:07:35,240 --> 01:07:36,760
- Move! Move!
- Come on! Come on!

1052
01:07:36,880 --> 01:07:38,120
Aren't you playing, huh, Yank?

1053
01:07:38,320 --> 01:07:40,080
Hey, kid. What are you doing here?

