- Hey, hey.

1056
01:07:44,760 --> 01:07:46,560
Hey, what're you trying to do?

1057
01:07:48,680 --> 01:07:51,960
Well, well, well. I'm...
It's really my Darlin'.

1058
01:07:52,080 --> 01:07:55,400
- It's my Babe.
- Babe, here she is.

1059
01:07:55,520 --> 01:07:58,720
