1163
01:13:37,840 --> 01:13:39,720
- Come on, Yankee!
- Go, Yankee, go!

1164
01:13:39,840 --> 01:13:41,680
Oh, this is gonna be close, folks:

1165
01:13:41,800 --> 01:13:44,520
Hedley has come up with the ball
and looks to home plate:

1166
01:13:44,720 --> 01:13:47,560
- The fun's over, you little runt!
- Trip him! Somebody!

1167
01:13:47,680 --> 01:13:50,440
- The boy is not slowing down!
- Not this time, punk!

1168
01:13:50,560 --> 01:13:51,640
Slide!

1169
01:13:54,360 --> 01:13:55,920
Or not slide!

1170
01:14:02,760 --> 01:14:03,760
Safe!

1171
01:14:04,960 --> 01:14:06,600
- Way to go!
- All right, Yankee!

1172
01:14:06,720 --> 01:14:08,280
How about that kid, huh?

1173
01:14:08,400 --> 01:14:10,680
Oh, no! No!

1174
01:14:10,800 --> 01:14:12,520
That's a little Tiger if I ever seen
one.

1175
01:14:12,640 --> 01:14:15,040
He did it! That's my Yankee!

1176
01:14:15,160 --> 01:14:18,280
Yankee! Yankee! Yankee!

1177
01:14:18,600 --> 01:14:20,560
Hey, Yank! We're coming down!
We're coming down!

1178
01:14:20,680 --> 01:14:21,880
That's my friend!

1179
01:14:22,040 --> 01:14:23,040
Ow! Ow!

1180
01:14:23,960 --> 01:14:25,240
Oh, that's me.

1181
01:14:29,280 --> 01:14:32,520
- We did it, Darlin'.
- No, you did it.

1182
01:14:32,760 --> 01:14:34,400
Like Babe said,

1183
01:14:34,560 --> 01:14:37,320
"It's not the bat, it's the batter. "

1184
01:14:38,160 --> 01:14:40,800
Listen to them, kid! They love you!

1185
01:14:40,920 --> 01:14:43,000
They're cheering for you, too,
Screwie!

1186
01:14:43,200 --> 01:14:46,280
Can you believe it? I'm a home run
ball!

1187
01:14:46,640 --> 01:14:48,320
Yahoo!

1188
01:14:49,360 --> 01:14:50,840
You always were.

1189
01:14:53,760 --> 01:14:55,440
Way to go, kid.

1190
01:14:59,440 --> 01:15:00,760
Thanks, Babe.

1191
01:15:03,160 --> 01:15:04,520
Yankee.
Yankee.

1192
01:15:04,720 --> 01:15:06,200
- Yankee.
- Yankee.

1193
01:15:08,040 --> 01:15:09,720
Mom! Dad!

1194
01:15:09,840 --> 01:15:14,480
- I did it, Dad. I did it.
- I always knew you could do it.

1195
01:15:14,600 --> 01:15:17,600
- You just kept swinging.
- Just like you taught me, Dad.

